, agreeing with the characteristics indicated for the female of 
<taxonomicName id="F8AC33DFFFEEB373CEE9F92C361EF959" box="[720,843,1724,1748]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="134" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="diversa">
